{"results":[{"aya":"155","id":3087,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"他说：这是一只母驼，它应得一部分饮料，你们应得某定日的一部分饮料。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"156","id":3088,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"你们不可伤害它，否则，将遭受重大日的惩罚。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"157","id":3089,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"但他们宰了它，随后，他们深觉悔恨。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"158","id":3090,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"但他们还是受了惩罚。此中确有一个迹象，但他们大半是不信道的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"159","id":3091,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"你的主，确是万能的，确是至慈的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"160","id":3092,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"鲁特的宗族，曾否认使者。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"161","id":3093,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"当日，他们的弟兄鲁特曾对他们说：你们怎么不敬畏呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":33,"previousPage":"/zh/s026-22.json","nextPage":"/zh/s026-24.json"}}